title: What serif typeface is this logo based on?
content:
What serif typeface is the Automatic Eye logo based on? Many thanks.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20130817213837im_/http:/typophile.com/files/sample_5313.png)
author: spirelli

comments.content:
It's an exact match to **[Ginebra Bolds](http://web.archive.org/web/20130817213837/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-1&ffam=Ginebra%20Bolds%20-%20Regular&fid=79d989fcbf1a7d6ad3ae4a7cd6e492ff&fsize=60&text=automatic%20eye&fit=1)** by Sohokid (2007, Free for personal use)

------------------  
I found it using "Find my Font": [http://www.findmyfont.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20130817213837/http:/www.findmyfont.com/ "http://www.findmyfont.com")
